uk.co.strangeskies.reflection.token

Interface ReifiedToken<S extends ReifiedToken<S>>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The type of the instance
    All Superinterfaces:
    Copyable<S>, Reified, Self<S>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TypedObject, TypeParameter, TypeToken

    public interface ReifiedToken<S extends ReifiedToken<S>>
extends Reified, Self<S>
    A type whose instances know their own type, including any available generic information.

    As with the extended Self interface, generally only the most specific useful type will be considered.

      • getThisType

        default Type getThisType()
        Specified by:
        getThisType in interface Reified
        Returns:
        The accurate type of the instance, accounting for generics. It is up to the implementation whether the returned type is also completely precise - in other words, the type may mention wildcards or inference variables if the exact type cannot be determined, and may not reflect the most specific possible class.
